a semantic variable i.e color-dark or color-light. This poses a problem

for the use of legacy_mappings as we only map "color" not "color-light"

meaning some subset of UI ignores a specified mapping.

problem autogenerated -rgb vars but this is left for a future CL

since it's a more involved change.

entry.title: Split PresentationRequestNotification{Producer,Item}
entry.content:
Split the classes across Mojo boundaries, in preparation of using them across the crosapi.



Factor out new classes from them that live on the Ash side of the split (or just in the same browser process in the case of other platforms):



- SupplementalDevicePickerProducer

implements mojom::DevicePickerProvider and MediaItemProducer



- SupplementalDevicePickerItem

implements MediaNotificationItem



The above classes are generalized and have no Cast/presentation-specific logic.



That logic is left in PRNP/PRNI which stay on the Lacros/browser side:



- PresentationRequestNotificationProducer

implements mojom::DevicePickerObserver



- PresentationRequestNotificationItem
